<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="165">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ou-yang-ying-61" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ou-yang-ying-61" class="zg-link" title="欧阳颖">欧阳颖</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-rui-99" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-rui-99" class="zg-link" title="李睿">李睿</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dan-ping-ao-qi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dan-ping-ao-qi" class="zg-link" title="但凭傲气">但凭傲气</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3036554" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><b>效果图：</b><br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/56d953c7d70ba98d5933195232532e31_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/56d953c7d70ba98d5933195232532e31_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/56d953c7d70ba98d5933195232532e31_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/56d953c7d70ba98d5933195232532e31_b.jpg"><br><br><b>素材：</b><br><br>1）题主提供的蝙蝠侠。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/4e8fcc664c70b43486097a232f4d39c3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/4e8fcc664c70b43486097a232f4d39c3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="337" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/4e8fcc664c70b43486097a232f4d39c3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/4e8fcc664c70b43486097a232f4d39c3_b.jpg"><br>2）木♂吉Kazuya<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/eb98601440b3b13aced3928ab6d14851_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/eb98601440b3b13aced3928ab6d14851_b.jpg"><br><br>为什么不是Van？<br>因为没有角度合适的。<br><br><br><br><b>方法：</b><br><br>1&gt; 建立图层蒙版，用“钢笔工具”把蝙蝠侠要露出的地方勾勒出来。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/aea655c87155454dfa7c8be5badebc0e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1008" data-rawheight="590" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1008" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/aea655c87155454dfa7c8be5badebc0e_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1008" data-rawheight="590" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1008" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/aea655c87155454dfa7c8be5badebc0e_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/aea655c87155454dfa7c8be5badebc0e_b.jpg"><br><br>2&gt; 从路径建立选区，把选中部分涂黑。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/2bdb92c7fe8ccf813644406aa4cecf59_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="165" data-rawheight="26" class="content_image" width="165"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="165" data-rawheight="26" class="content_image lazy" width="165" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/2bdb92c7fe8ccf813644406aa4cecf59_b.jpg"><br>3&gt; 把木吉的照片图层放在蝙蝠侠的图层下面，调整位置和角度。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/0aaa4f3a5510826560ec85733bba7f54_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1008" data-rawheight="590" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1008" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/0aaa4f3a5510826560ec85733bba7f54_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1008" data-rawheight="590" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1008" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/0aaa4f3a5510826560ec85733bba7f54_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/0aaa4f3a5510826560ec85733bba7f54_b.jpg"><br>4&gt; 把蝙蝠侠胸前的蝙蝠标志抠出来，复制图层并调成半透明。<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/7bf6ad83686f104b045a640f6261ec08_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="171" data-rawheight="112" class="content_image" width="171"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="171" data-rawheight="112" class="content_image lazy" width="171" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/7bf6ad83686f104b045a640f6261ec08_b.jpg"><br>5&gt; 调整肉体的饱和度，使与背景的灰暗色调匹配，即得效果图。边缘细节、光阴效果可根据需要继续优化。<br><br>6&gt; 诚念哲♂学三信：<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/c684374c5ada476abe4db216b4da3164_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="550" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="550" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/c684374c5ada476abe4db216b4da3164_b.jpg"><br><br>以下摘自：<a href="http://zh.moegirl.org/%E5%93%B2%E2%99%82%E5%AD%A6" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">哲♂学 - 萌娘百科 万物皆可萌的百科全书<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br>哲♂学三信<blockquote><p>哲学三信是哲学思想的大原则和绝对普遍真理。包含了以下三个部分：</p><p>告诫之心：你还做得不够好啊！</p><p>赞美之心：你做得很不错嘛！</p><p>宽容之心：那也是没有办法的事情嘛！</p><p>三者合称“戒赞许”，是每一个哲学信徒必须要熟知和遵守的内容。</p><p>没有遵守哲学三信的兄贵动画和信徒都不算是真正的粉丝，能够理解它的人才是真正的兄贵爱好者。</p><p>参透哲学三信，则是兄贵哲学的最高境界。</p></blockquote>


</div>

</div>
